{"tid":1853983,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"部macbook係咪收皮了？","createTime":"2020-01-31T09:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T09:42:39.000Z","uid":122936,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"df6f706a3639283e8d8a9317e06e942b0a68c4c6","tid":1853983,"uid":122936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:20:45.000Z","msg":"用緊macbook air，本身用緊買電腦送三年既kaspersky防毒軟件。最近過咗期就諗住down翻學校免費既NOD32。<br />\n我down個陣電腦提示話要del左kaspersky先，如果唔係會crash。我就del啦，但del完down咗之後部機就lag到用唔到。<br />\n我重新開機左幾次都係好lag，然後kaspersky個過期提示仲彈出黎，係咪姐係冇del到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家lag到safari google chrome都用唔到，㩒一下lag半分鐘以上。。點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申電腦白痴港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e737b470d13e302579fddb140b45efe693c393","tid":1853983,"uid":79615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:22:37.000Z","msg":"洗機"},{"pid":"c82ab5e9533a80943972628f796382de70a7a577","tid":1853983,"uid":36673,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:22:44.000Z","msg":"Mac用防毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等啲有愛心嘅人入黎救你"},{"pid":"18fc128c554749f2782abef3343e29feec76b0a3","tid":1853983,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:24:52.000Z","msg":"似係2隻防毒程式撞左"},{"pid":"21c5883151c8cacd7a92f5f6df42201724f9e803","tid":1853983,"uid":122936,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c82ab5e9533a80943972628f796382de70a7a577","tid":1853983,"uid":36673,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:22:44.000Z","msg":"Mac用防毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等啲有愛心嘅人入黎救你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:25:50.000Z","msg":"我唔識電腦野 成日驚中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5f1788b9ebf4f995063991b43f032eda0c98b3","tid":1853983